 the S\\~ao Paulo potential,\nwhereas the spectroscopic amplitudes for the projectile and target overlaps\nwere derived from shell-model calculations. The theoretical cross sections are\nfound to be in very good agreement with the experimental data, suggesting the\nvalidity of the optical potentials and the shell-model description of the\ninvolved nuclear states within the adopted model space.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 20 Oct 2021 16:24:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-22"}
