ound that maximum of radio power falls therefore in\nthe range 4 to 10 $R_{\\odot}$, depending on whether the type III emissions are\nassumed to be at the fundamental or the harmonic.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 21 Oct 2021 07:08:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-01-19"}
