h previous STAR measurements\nand with predictions from current next-to-leading order global analyses. They\nprovide more precise data at low dijet invariant mass that will better\nconstraint the shape of the polarized gluon distribution function of the\nproton.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 21 Oct 2021 09:55:24 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 23 May 2022 18:02:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-05-25"}
